Washington 28 fair.
   _Central: Bismarck 8 fair; Dallas-Fort Worth 34 cloudy; Denver 22
fair; Des Moines 26 fair; Indianapolis 22 fair; Kansas City 33
cloudy; Minneapolis-St. Paul 31 windy; Nashville 36 cloudy; New
Orleans 53 drizzle; St. Louis 30 partly cloudy.
