Los Angeles 49 fair; Phoenix 45 fair; Salt Lake City 12 fair; San
Diego 48 fair; San Francisco 44 partly cloudy; Seattle 35 windy.
   _Canada: Montreal 12 fair; Toronto 19 fair.
