<HEAD>Child Barred From Court After Pretending to Shoot Murder Victim's
Daughter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LAWRENCEVILLE, Ga. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An 8-year-old girl, whose older brother
was on trial for murder, was barred from a courtroom and surrounding
